INSERT INTO exhibition VALUES ('2019-08-18 12:00:00','2019-05-14 12:00:00','https://d32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net/YbS4c5FVFoHIV4vYqXkWiA/medium.jpg','A vast throng of animals tumble, soar, and race through the pages of the bestiary, a popular medieval book describing the beasts of the world. With over 100 works on display, this major loan exhibition transports visitors into the world of the medieval bestiary.','5d324eba09d053000e982935','Book of Beasts: The Bestiary in the Medieval World',NULL,'5139fa9d03a8b33748000004',3);
INSERT INTO exhibition VALUES ('2019-10-13 12:00:00','2019-06-11 12:00:00','https://d32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net/Cbj6Yd5D2COBHEOUqCUk7g/medium.jpg','The Bauhaus was a German school of art and design whose brief yet highly influential existence rendered it a key site in the development of a new modern vision for arts education. Established in 1919, this exhibition marks the one hundredth anniversary of the school’s opening. ','5d325af159a08b000e4b18a2','Bauhaus Beginnings',NULL,'5139fa9d03a8b33748000004',3);
INSERT INTO exhibition VALUES ('2019-10-28 12:00:00','2019-06-26 12:00:00','https://d32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net/Xak3nz2GgA280y_fxGQ8gw/medium.jpg','The Getty Villa is modeled on the Villa dei Papiri at Herculaneum. Buried by the eruption of Mount Vesuvius in AD 79, the ancient villa was later rediscovered. This exhibition presents rare original artifacts and traces attempts to unroll and decipher the carbonized papyri.','5d375d27eef9c0000de9fe92','Buried by Vesuvius: Treasures from the Villa dei Papiri',NULL,'5139fa9d03a8b33748000004',3);
INSERT INTO exhibition VALUES ('2019-11-10 12:00:00','2019-07-09 12:00:00','https://d32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net/OH3nntEhXDKLay40q5_N_w/medium.jpg','On assignment to document poverty in Brazil for Life magazine, American photographer Gordon Parks encountered one of the most important subjects of his career: Flávio da Silva. This exhibition explores his celebrated photo essay and Parks’ representation of Flávio over decades.','5d377ca0bd7de3000e5ce76b','Gordon Parks: The Flávio Story',NULL,'5139fa9d03a8b33748000004',3);
INSERT INTO exhibition VALUES ('2019-01-27 12:00:00','2018-08-25 12:00:00','https://d32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net/2uNo6mFofBHNiPRJHwJjIQ/medium.jpg','The large-scale paintings by Argentine-Swiss artist Vivian Suter will transform Kenneth and Anne Griffin Court at the Art Institute of Chicago. Suter installs her work as an immersive interior that mirrors the exterior of her home: the Guatemalan rainforest.','5d55a8925c7dee0015552fb9','Vivian Suter: el bosque interior',NULL,'50d20b9e6e23ab206c000a60',3);
